ygData.subject: RE: [EverQuest] Ranger comparison
ygData.msgSnippet: Life will pick up when you hit 9 and get spells.  I also suggest that you just look at most other people your level / class and ask where they got their stuff.
ygData.messageBody:
Life will pick up when you hit 9 and get spells. I also suggest that you
just look at most other people your level / class and ask where they got
their stuff.

oh...and a good shield to get for you is the Shiny Brass Shield...

Just kill the Taskmaster in Crushbone for it...or buy it for the average
10-15pp :>
